##Pokemon Trivia
A game for guessing who is that Pokemon

##Usage
Your main pages would be the index files for both user and admin

poke_index.php and admin_index.php

A mongo database is needed where users will be added when registering.
Admin account is created in a seperate document.
json file is provided to import pokemon into your database

pokemon_array.json

User points will accunmulate and badged will brighten when you get a certain number correct
User's will need to get atleast 151 correct to collect all badges.

##Contributing
Pull requests are welcome





